{
  "stem": "18581.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 360.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I had a hunch why I was invited, because normally, you give such an honor to an uncle or a father or-- or an important person or the priest.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was given it because some people said, lets do it, because the priest says that he's related to the bishop and he's a refugee and we should help him, but he kind of has sad eyes.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He looks like a Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he doesn't speak like a Jew, said.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They said, OK, so we don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So let's give him this test.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they gave me the test.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the same morning I prayed in Hebrew secretly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then I went to the party.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And of course, I-- I took a big knife and I hit the pig right into the throat, where I was supposed to, because I've seen the ceremony in Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't have to drink the blood before the war, because everybody knew I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This time, I drank the blood would great gusto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I don't know how I swallowed it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And everybody else joined in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And on the way back, when everybody was drunk from locally made liquor, my host said that-- don't feel so, so big.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's not because you are a teacher or because you are so smart.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Simply they wanted to use this as a test to see if you are Jewish or not.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And thank god you're not.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had false papers from the priest Gediminas Peletskis.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But of course, these were not-- these were papers of a village priest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe Aleksas Tautkus.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A-L-E-K-S-A-S Tautkus, T-A-U-T-K-U-S.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, whenever Germans used to approach the-- the farm, I used to-- from the back, I always-- I had my place prepared.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
